BI Dashboard:

This folder contains the Business Intelligence dashboard developed
to visualize and analyze processed e-commerce data.

Tools:
- Power BI Desktop

Data Sources:
The dashboard consumes processed Excel datasets generated in the
`2_data_processing` module, including standardized mapping files (MAPs).

Key Insights:
The dashboard enables analysis of:
- Sales performance
- Product distribution
- Geographic trends
- Channel and category breakdowns

Refresh Logic:
The dashboard is refreshed after executing the scraping and
data processing workflows, ensuring updated insights.

Files:
- `.pbix` file: main Power BI dashboard
- Preview images: visual reference of dashboard pages
